comments: Collins (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in McLemore's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
McLemore (HOU) makes marginal body contact with Young (ATL) after he has returned to the floor following the jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Hunter (ATL) is the last player to touch the ball prior to the out of bounds.
Huerter (ATL) makes marginal contact Gordon's (HOU) front and side during his drive into the lane.
Len (ATL) makes marginal contact to Tucker's (HOU) body during his shot at the rim.
Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact to Young (ATL) at the start of his drive to the basket.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Len's (ATL) lower body during the put-back.
Hunter makes marginal contact with his forearm to Harden's side during the drive.
Collins (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position along  Harden's (HOU) path during his drive and kick.
Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact with Young's (ATL) body prior to Harden (HOU) cleanly dislodging the ball during the shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) moves laterally and initiates contact to Harden's (HOU) side/front that affects his SQBR.
Len (ATL) makes marginal contact with Capela's (HOU) left arm during rebounding.
Tucker (HOU) makes marginal contact with Collins' (ATL) right arm during rebounding.
As Tucker (HOU) is falling out of bounds in an attempt to retrieve the rebound, Hunter (ATL) makes incidental contact with his side.
Gordon (HOU) makes contact with Len's (ATL) arm during his upward shooting motion affecting his shot near the rim.
Huerter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Gordon's (HOU) side as he dribbles up the court along the sideline.
Reddish (ATL) commits the take foul on Harden (HOU).
Gordon (HOU) briefly places his arm around Young's (ATL) midsection before correcting.
Young (ATL) makes some contact with his off-arm to Tucker's (HOU) front along the perimeter, but it is marginal.
Hunter (ATL) commits the take foul on Harden (HOU).
